{"tid":778971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全港十大垃圾屋村】良景邨姐弟嘈交 警救出家姐拉藏毒弟","createTime":"2018-08-14T05:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T07:44:11.000Z","uid":160807,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ecec6b8a63de4c7279f6b659b4ad5418a3059716","tid":778971,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180813/large/1534138901_72ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180813%2Flarge%2F1534138901_72ef.jpg&h=69dcfb16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180813/large/1534138874_09d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180813%2Flarge%2F1534138874_09d3.jpg&h=73a33eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屯門良景邨良英樓，中午近12時，有鄰居聽到其中一單位傳出女子叫救命聲，擔心下報警求助，警員接報大為緊張，持盾牌登樓，發現肇事單位有兩姐弟因家庭瑣事爭執，有人情緒激動，胞姊被打受傷，胞弟則被揭發藏毒被捕，受傷胞姊送院敷治，警員將胞弟帶署時，連同其行李篋一併撿走調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180813/58557093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58557093&d=GoBdzZCraoQEJw9QjDPyFHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=cf957c5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58557093&h=da5f555d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180813/58557093</a>"},{"pid":"c569e4209d52165ee52fc7b6fa465774d0e4b2fc","tid":778971,"uid":4826,"like":10,"dislike":13,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"屯元天都係比垃圾住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f903f645764d3b74c566898d46bef299a8687ec","tid":778971,"uid":73340,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-1